## Auth Flow
/login → magic link / Google / GitHub OAuth → /auth/callback → has org? / : /onboarding
Onboarding: Haiku-guided Q&A (5 exchanges) → structured context JSON → saved to organisations.context → confirm card → home
Invite system: settings form (role picker, seat limit check) → pending invite → auth callback auto-activates on first login

