## Critical Patterns
Server client: const supabase = await createServerSupabaseClient()
Anon client for all data queries (RLS enforces scoping), service role only for users + org_members
Assistant request: { message, history } → response: { reply, history } — rolling 6-message window to AI
Full conversation history saved to conversations table, 24h session restore
Any new Date() in JSX needs suppressHydrationWarning
Sidebar home link: href="/" active only when pathname === "/"
Tracking tab links: /tracking?tab=contacts and /tracking?tab=companies
Kanban: drag-drop persists via PATCH /api/deals/[id]/stage, save/discard bar, amber pending state
Analytics layout: dnd-kit cross-column drag, DragOverlay ghost, ResizeObserver responsive charts, edit/save/cancel mode persisted to org context

